## Exploration Complete

I've mapped all three summarizer files. Here's the cartography:

### Summary

| File | Type | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|
| **summarizer.go** | source | Package root: Client interface + ChatRequest/ChatMessage/result types |
| **service.go** | source | Service orchestrator: manages queue processing, calls Client interface, persists to storage |
| **service_test.go** | test | 16 test cases covering single messages, queue processing, API errors, time windows, local model config |

### Architecture
- `summarizer.go` defines the **Client interface** (abstraction for Ollama/OpenRouter implementations)
- `service.go` orchestrates via a 150-char threshold: short messages copy verbatim, long ones go to LLM
- Two queue strategies: all messages or filtered by channel IDs
- Time window: today + yesterday UTC
- Queue stops on first API error (records partial progress)

